{"desi_lesson":{"title":"Weather & Seasons","target_language":"Kannada","theme":"Weather & Seasons","vocabulary":[{"english":"Sun","target_language_script":"ಸೂರ್ಯ","transliteration":"soorya","pronunciation":"soo-ryuh"},{"english":"Rain","target_language_script":"ಮಳೆ","transliteration":"male","pronunciation":"muh-ley"},{"english":"Wind","target_language_script":"ಗಾಳಿ","transliteration":"gaali","pronunciation":"gah-lee"},{"english":"Hot","target_language_script":"ಬಿಸಿಲು","transliteration":"bisilu","pronunciation":"bi-si-lu"},{"english":"Cold","target_language_script":"ತಣ್ಣಗಿದೆ","transliteration":"tannugide","pronunciation":"tun-nuh-gi-dey"},{"english":"Summer","target_language_script":"ಬೇಸಿಗೆ","transliteration":"besige","pronunciation":"bey-si-gey"},{"english":"Winter","target_language_script":"ಚಳಿಗಾಲ","transliteration":"chaligala","pronunciation":"chuh-li-gah-luh"},{"english":"Rainy season","target_language_script":"ಮಳೆಗಾಲ","transliteration":"malegala","pronunciation":"muh-ley-gah-luh"},{"english":"Cloudy","target_language_script":"ಮೋಡ","transliteration":"moda","pronunciation":"moh-dah"},{"english":"weather","target_language_script":"ಹವಾಮಾನ","transliteration":"havamaana","pronunciation":"huh-vah-mah-nah"}],"example_sentences":[{"english":"The sun is shining.","target_language_script":"ಸೂರ್ಯ ಬಿಸಿಲಾಗಿದೆ.","transliteration":"soorya bisilaagide.","pronunciation":"soo-ryuh bi-si-lah-gi-dey."},{"english":"It is raining.","target_language_script":"ಮಳೆಯಾಗುತ್ತಿದೆ.","transliteration":"maleyaaguttide.","pronunciation":"muh-ley-ah-gu-ti-dey."},{"english":"The wind is blowing.","target_language_script":"ಗಾಳಿ ಬೀಸುತ್ತಿದೆ.","transliteration":"gaali beesuttide.","pronunciation":"gah-lee bee-su-ti-dey."},{"english":"It is very hot today.","target_language_script":"ಇಂದು ತುಂಬಾ ಬಿಸಿಲು.","transliteration":"indu tumba bisilu.","pronunciation":"in-doo tum-bah bi-si-lu."},{"english":"It's cold in the winter.","target_language_script":"ಚಳಿಗಾಲದಲ್ಲಿ ತಣ್ಣಗಿರುತ್ತದೆ.","transliteration":"chaligaladaalli tannugiruttade.","pronunciation":"chuh-li-gah-luh-dal-lee tun-nuh-gi-ru-tu-dey."}],"short_story":{"title":"The Changing Weather","dialogue":[{"speaker":"Person A","target_language_script":"ಇಂದು ಬಿಸಿಲು ಇದೆ.","transliteration":"Indu bisilu ide.","english":"It's sunny today."},{"speaker":"Person B","target_language_script":"ಹೌದು, ಆದರೆ ಗಾಳಿ ಬೀಸುತ್ತಿದೆ.","transliteration":"Haadu, aadare gaali beesuttide.","english":"Yes, but the wind is blowing."},{"speaker":"Person A","target_language_script":"ಮಳೆಗಾಲ ಬರುತ್ತಿದೆ ಎಂದು ಕೇಳಿದೆ.","transliteration":"Malegala baruttide endu keli.","english":"I heard the rainy season is coming."}]},"quiz":[{"question":"How do you say 'sun' in Kannada?","options":["male","soorya","gaali","bisilu"],"answer":"soorya"},{"question":"What is the Kannada word for 'rain'?","options":["soorya","male","besige","chaligala"],"answer":"male"},{"question":"How do you say 'cold' in Kannada?","options":["bisilu","tannugide","havamaana","moda"],"answer":"tannugide"},{"question":"What is the Kannada word for 'summer'?","options":["chaligala","malegala","besige","gaali"],"answer":"besige"}]}}